{"tid":1641184,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"熱烈呼籲各位模型友黎瘋狂懲罰呢間高質模型耗材店","createTime":"2019-10-09T09:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T04:58:12.000Z","uid":60470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9efd6f9498e141b1650dbaa3bb26284f5f40959","tid":1641184,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"以前都有去開，今日上開去見老闆同另一個阿叔傾緊時事，本來仲驚佢如果係藍絲咁點算<br />\n點知兩位都非常明事理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全唔係街邊阿叔之流，搞到我忍唔住買多左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老闆平時已經好nice，貨又齊，大家話係咪要密啲上去清哂佢啲貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4f58a6d62c1a40b5797578d6648f38edaee664","tid":1641184,"uid":31738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"買油噴高達貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6a8752f84070731fd699ca44c5df584e1c44a5","tid":1641184,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】隊㝝WeChat妙法！借警察報料熱線一齊將騰訊列美國制裁名單！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情請閱：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1641145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1641145</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chrsTee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchrsTee.jpg&h=60437086&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca3641155fd8897f4c3d43d8d4933a490fc94fe5","tid":1641184,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d4f58a6d62c1a40b5797578d6648f38edaee664","tid":1641184,"uid":31738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"買油噴高達貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"平有平玩，可以上去慢慢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者放膽問下老細<br />\n老闆真係乜鬼都有，包括呢支斷哂貨既新款消光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（上消光個面都照可以保持光滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n淨係消光就62一支，夠你整四五盒"},{"pid":"0709dc1f1fc7ad54503a5d22ed0b80550b244545","tid":1641184,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d4f58a6d62c1a40b5797578d6648f38edaee664","tid":1641184,"uid":31738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"買油噴高達貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"呢間啲油都平<br />\n不過唔多齊色<br />\n但都有成櫃比人揀(好多牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n耗材，工具好齊"},{"pid":"f12e186169e179fe09a45ce60cd30a9848370cf8","tid":1641184,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca3641155fd8897f4c3d43d8d4933a490fc94fe5","tid":1641184,"uid":60470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d4f58a6d62c1a40b5797578d6648f38edaee664","tid":1641184,"uid":31738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"買油噴高達貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"平有平玩，可以上去慢慢執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者放膽問下老細<br />\n老闆真係乜鬼都有，包括呢支斷哂貨既新款消光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（上消光個面都照可以保持光滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n淨係消光就62一支，夠你整四五盒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"漏左圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0Ccj4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0Ccj4H.jpg&h=7a7c3518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e4953d6ab1486affbf48471885eca7b92f5784c","tid":1641184,"uid":216982,"l